  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "RELATIONSHIP MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attend to all walk-in residents, including updating feedback provider on the action taken;</li>\n  <li>Utilise system to check past feedback cases or create new cases;</li>\n  <li>Issue events/facilities booking permits as and when required;</li>\n  <li>Reply to feedback emails &amp; calls;</li>\n  <li>Attend to cases on site (including house visit), where required/instructed;</li>\n  <li>First responder for any escalated cases;</li>\n  <li>Communicate with external agencies for cases;</li>\n  <li>Any other duties as instructed by the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experienced in handling difficult people;</li>\n  <li>Possess good interpersonal skills;</li>\n  <li>Work well under pressure;</li>\n  <li>Effective written &amp; verbal communication;</li>\n  <li>Must be able to attend cases on site independently;</li>\n  <li>IT savvy;</li>\n  <li>Working Hours: Mondays - Fridays: 8am to 5pm with an additional 1 Saturday per month - 8am to 1pm;</li>\n  <li>Work Location: please refer to this link: https://www.ahtc.sg/town-council-offices/</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
