    "description": "<p>The Town Council manages HDB estates in Aljunied GRC and Hougang SMC. More than 50,000 dwelling units, shops, hawker stalls come under our purview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To serve our residents well, there is a team of about 100 dedicated staff in Estate management, Admin, Finance, IT, Human resources, Tender and Contracts, and Public Relations. At the core of the management is a holistic of elected members and town councillors and community leaders with a wide range of experiences and competencies.</p>\r\n",
